{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 200°C. Grease a casserole dish (30 x 20 cm) and set aside.","Place a bowl onto mixing bowl lid, then weigh red lentils into it. Add enough water to cover lentils and set aside to soak for 2 hours.","Place Parmesan into mixing bowl and grate <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place olive oil, onion, garlic and capsicum into mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>.","Add tomatoes (including liquid) and mix <b>2 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add red wine, oregano, ginger, salt and pepper and cook <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>.","Place Varoma into position, then arrange eggplant slices into it, ensuring steam can circulate freely. Secure Varoma lid and steam <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Remove Varoma and set aside.","Drain lentils through simmering basket. Add drained lentils to mixing bowl and cook <b>7 min\/100°C\/\/speed 2<b>.","Transfer steamed eggplant slices into the base of prepared casserole dish, then top with lentil mixture. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place butter, milk and flour into mixing bowl and cook <b>8 min\/90°C\/speed 4<b>.","Add 60 g of the reserved Parmesan and mix <b>5 sec\/speed 4<b>.","Transfer cheese sauce into casserole dish and sprinkle with remaining reserved Parmesan. Bake for 30 minutes (200°C) or until top is lightly golden brown. Cut moussaka into squares and serve hot."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["40 g butter, plus extra for greasing","200 g dried red lentils","water, for soaking","120 g Parmesan cheese, cut into cubes (3 cm)","50 g olive oil","1 brown onion (approx. 150 g), cut into quarters","3 garlic cloves","1 red capsicum, deseeded and cut into pieces","400 g canned whole tomatoes (including liquid)","120 g red wine","1 sprig fresh oregano, leaves only","1 tsp ground ginger","2 tsp sea salt","½ tsp ground black pepper","1 eggplant (approx. 550 g), cut into slices (1 cm)","500 g full cream milk","40 g spelt flour"]}],"id":"r71139","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-Fs4nbf_zYtU\/XZWZLFLbfWI\/AAAAAAAAeI4\/YxOljOameFkr_VHg8jHvB_8wdYdEvQDjgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_VfmHAxNDn43wJPdB.png","title":"Lentil moussaka","publishedAt":"2014-07-22T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"22.6 g","fat":"23.8 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"35 g","calories":"1997.7 kJ \/ 475.7 kcal"},"usefulItems":"casserole dish (30 x 20 cm), bowl, oven","basicInfo":["easy","25m","3h 30m","6 portions"]}